cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.CV, cs.RO 

The paper presents a learning environment for machine learning agents based on the video game Toribash. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The environment involves two humanoid characters fighting each other hand-to-hand, which suggests it could also belong to the sub-category of Graphics (cs.GR). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of computer vision techniques to extract features from the game, which could place it in the sub-category of Computer Vision (cs.CV). Finally, the environment involves controlling the joints of the characters, which could also place it in the sub-category of Robotics (cs.RO).
